{"tid":2294393,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Monkey國：旅遊氣泡照去馬 但香港旅客抵埗後要檢測","createTime":"2020-11-21T03:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T04:01:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1efe6c43927b17ab644c0d1da705dfa6faaf3c98","tid":2294393,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:51:28.000Z","msg":"新港航空泡泡明天（22日）將如期起航，但在此計劃下從香港入境我國的所有乘客，抵境後必須在樟宜機場接受聚合酶鏈反應（PCR）檢測。<br />\n<br />\n香港的2019冠狀病毒疾病疫情近日趨向嚴重，原定在明天啓動的新港航空泡泡能否如期舉行，受到許多人關注。<br />\n新加坡民航局今天（21日）在文告中說，明天起通過航空泡泡到我國的乘客必須在樟宜機場接受PCR檢測，這額外要求是一項預防措施，因為香港的冠病病例過去幾天有所增加。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n乘客在進行檢測後，必須到酒店或本地居民家中隔離大約六到八個小時，直到檢測結果出爐。<br />\n</span><br />\n文告說，PCR檢測費用為196元。在額外措施實行的第一個星期，入境者無需支付檢測費。<br />\n<br />\n因為疫情再次出現反彈，香港政府已宣佈從明天起收緊防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/ong-yee-kung-on-travel-bubble-1316371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.8world.com%2Fnews%2Fsingapore%2Farticle%2Fong-yee-kung-on-travel-bubble-1316371&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM37ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=d4cf2737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.8world.com/news/singapore/article/ong-yee-kung-on-travel-bubble-1316371</a>"},{"pid":"eac3cc798419183d6f2fe07fd138a04a82d36365","tid":2294393,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98eb38bac6e9703c1e3390a3429cdd2dfbe3c094","tid":2294393,"uid":304769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T03:57:02.000Z","msg":"去睇monkey都要檢疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab28dee79173c1598431d85c69f2672bcb564c5","tid":2294393,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}